16 (iv) property tax exemptions; or
17 (iv)(v) any other matter in which the appeal is provided by law.
18 (2) A person may appeal the department's annual assessment of an industrial property to the
19 Montana board as provided in this section or to the county tax appeal board for the county in which the property
